Package: siomon
Architecture: amd64 arm64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Linux hardware information and sensor monitoring tool
 siomon provides comprehensive Linux hardware information and real-time
 sensor monitoring as a single static binary. It supports detailed hardware
 inventory (CPU, GPU, memory, storage, motherboard, network) and real-time
 sensor monitoring with an interactive terminal interface.
 .
 Output formats include text, JSON, XML, HTML, and CSV. The tool gracefully
 degrades when not running as root and has zero mandatory runtime
 dependencies.
